Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.map.mutable.primitive

Class SynchronizedIntDoubleMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.map.mutable.primitive.SynchronizedIntDoubleMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, DoubleIterable, DoubleValuesMap, IntDoubleMap, MutableDoubleValuesMap, MutableIntDoubleMap, PrimitiveIterable
    public class SynchronizedIntDoubleMap
extends Object
implements MutableIntDoubleMap, Serializable
    A synchronized view of a MutableIntDoubleMap. It is imperative that the user manually synchronize on the collection when iterating over it using the MutableDoubleIterator as per Collections.synchronizedCollection(Collection).

    This file was automatically generated from template file synchronizedPrimitivePrimitiveMap.stg.

    Since:
    3.1.
    See Also:
    MutableIntDoubleMap.asSynchronized(), MutableMap.asSynchronized(), Serialized Form
